            <title>讯飞输入法崩了，官方回应：端午节活动配置出现 Bug，升级新版本即可恢复</title>
            <description>&lt;div class=&quot;tougao-user&quot;&gt;感谢 IT 之家网友 &lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1865992&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;软媒用户 1865992&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D375533&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;冲葱&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1642737&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Alphonisorca&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D831895&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;洗个痛快澡&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1561882&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;反反反复复复&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1133406&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;n_newen&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1671489&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;格式化大法&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D276951&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;雷震子&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1761474&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;凌子傲&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1802554&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;无名可取甚烦&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1387764&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;司马不平&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1165946&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;村口李大爷&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1754465&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;木南冰室打杂&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1769432&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;境界随想&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1937885&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Apllo&lt;/a&gt; 的线索投递！&lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;p data-vmark=&quot;4dac&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;s_tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.ithome.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;IT 之家&lt;/a&gt; 6 月 5 日消息，今日晚间，大量 IT 之家网友反馈称讯飞输入法出现故障，包括但不限于输入框无法弹出、显示断网等。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-vmark=&quot;bd07&quot;&gt;讯飞输入法官方回应称：讯飞输入法在配置端午节运营活动过程中出现 Bug，导致部分用户出现客户端崩溃问题。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-vmark=&quot;d3b9&quot;&gt;对此，输入法团队正在对此进行全力抢修，6 月 5 日晚会发布新版本修复问题，新版本发布后、升级版本可恢复使用。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot; data-vmark=&quot;46d3&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/6/b195a055-c864-44d1-a799-89ae6496fa6b.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto&quot; w=&quot;635&quot; h=&quot;171&quot; title=&quot;讯飞输入法崩了，官方回应：端午节活动配置出现 Bug，升级新版本即可恢复&quot; width=&quot;635&quot; height=&quot;171&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-vmark=&quot;26df&quot;&gt;截至 IT 之家发稿，目前讯飞输入法仍显示为三天前更新的 13.1.1 版本，如果有遇到此类 Bug 的用户可以等晚些时候下载更新。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;ad-tips&quot;&gt;广告声明：文内含有的对外跳转链接（包括不限于超链接、二维码、口令等形式），用于传递更多信息，节省甄选时间，结果仅供参考，IT 之家所有文章均包含本声明。&lt;/p&gt;
        </description>
